<AbstractNarration>EIA-0079557&lt;br/&gt;Smith, Scott R.&lt;br/&gt;Southern Illinois University Edwardsville&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;MRI:  Acquisition of Immersive WorkWall System for Campus-wide Visualization Research&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;This proposal requests funds to provide Southern Illinois University at Edwardsville with the visualization capabilities of an Immersive WorkWall System.  The particular Immersive WorkWall consists of a single screen stereoscopic projection system and a workstation rendering dual graphic images onto a six by eight foot screen.  Viewers wearing special glasses experience real depth effects.  The new equipment capability will significantly enhance the on-going research activities concerning animated simulation models of scientific and engineering concepts.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
